{"tid":1223853,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(回帶，有圖有證據) 戀殖林鄭 公開承認全家與英國關係深厚！","createTime":"2019-06-14T21:40:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-15T07:53:50.000Z","uid":33933,"like":29,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"fd5f221c2105174cdb13792ae0e19098ef1d7203","tid":1223853,"uid":33933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T21:40:27.000Z","msg":"戀殖林鄭港英餘孽 <br />\n慶祝英女皇生日 懷念以前英女皇壽辰假期 同埋公開承認與英國關係深厚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢鑊仲唔係勾結英國 出賣中國既證據<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/http://fs.mingpao.com/pns/20180609/s00046/c63c25bad31b3d94cd68c8f7b4dd6ba4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F20180609%2Fs00046%2Fc63c25bad31b3d94cd68c8f7b4dd6ba4.jpg&h=57e7121b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n以下為明報於 2018年6月9號報導<br />\n<br />\n【明報專訊】今日係英女王官式壽辰，英國駐港總領事館噚日率先舉行酒會，為「事頭婆」英女王慶祝92歲生日，今年請咗訪港嘅女王幼子、54歲嘅愛德華王子，同埋<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">特首林鄭月娥做主禮嘉賓，兩人仲一齊切英國旗圖案蛋糕慶祝</span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭主禮 大談家人同英國淵源<br />\n<br />\n據Emily了解，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">前特首梁振英任內一次都無去過呢個酒會，而林鄭今次仲同埋幾個局長出席。林鄭致辭笑笑口提到，仲記得舊時英女王生日係公眾假期，講佢一家四口同英國關係深厚</span></span>，都曾經喺劍橋讀書，又提到佢曾經駐英工作一年半，恭喜英國王室近來喜事唔少，包括再添一個小公主。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.mingpaocanada.com/van/htm/News/20180609/HK-gzb1_r.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.mingpaocanada.com%2Fvan%2Fhtm%2FNews%2F20180609%2FHK-gzb1_r.htm&d=YB8lrFeyQ%2BkzHCEHpdql8JKhd8YmQljH21R%2F5cbT5WU%3D&h=d2a015ef\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.mingpaocanada.com/van/htm/News/20180609/HK-gzb1_r.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/pns/港聞/article/20180609/s00002/1528482035827/愛德華王子訪港-為英女王賀壽\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20180609%2Fs00002